<body>
  {{> header}}
  <main role="main" class="container">
    <p><strong>Progout</strong> - is a website created for studying tasks sharing. Teachers can share their courses
      on site and other users are able to get access to tasks of all shared courses, solve it themselves at home
      ot etc. and upload their solutions. Teacher can have access to all of uploaded solutions and give every of
      them a mark which will be available for solution`s author.</p>
    <p>Every registered user can look at common score table inside avery course.</p>
    <p>Such kind of website can be useful for online-study spreading. Students, solving tasks at home, will form skills
      of self-discipline and responsibility. A fact that student is not restricted at choise of information source also
      contributes to improving skill of studying material searching and process big amaout of new data.</p>
    <p>Because of fact that a ground of Progout`s concept is a responsible approach to solving studying tasks and to
      process of their evaluation it is possible to say that sharing of such a product in educational environment will
      have a good influence for a level of academic integrity.</p>
  </main>
  {{> footer}} {{> scripts}}
</body>

</html>